-- BB&T shares down after news of stock sale
-- 
-- Mon May 11, 2009 4:35pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/05/11/us-markets-stocks-bbt-sb-idUSTRE54A1XH20090511

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of BB&T Corp fell 6.6 percent to $24.60 in premarket trading on Monday, after the regional bank said it would sell $1.5 billion of stock and cut its dividend by 68 percent. 

 (Reporting by Ryan Vlastelica. Editing by Walker Simon)